      "span_text": "HKC8 cells, a human-derived renal proximal tubule cell line  , were cultured in DMEM/Ham's F-12 medium 1:1 mixture supplemented with 2.5% FCS, insulin-transferrin-selenium supplement (Gibco), and 2 mM glutamine."
